<span id="freeTextContainer5528386547973320965">4.5 stars. A beautifully written story about the prison testimony of Freddie Montgomery who killed a maid trying to stop him stealing a painting. Set in Ireland. Freddie writes about his mother, his wife and his friends/associates. A great character study. A book to reread.</span>

          </span>
